prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, flat 2D vector illustration. A humorous and charming beach scene. In the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are sitting cross-legged on a large, round beach blanket. Lao Lao, in her light blue sweatshirt, is hilariously attempting to build a sandcastle shaped like a giant takeout box of Chinese noodles. She has a look of intense, funny concentration, with tiny sand chopsticks sticking out of the top of the "box." Jordan, in his tan hoodie, is laughing and presenting her with an actual, perfectly detailed Chinese takeout box, complete with noodles and chopsticks, as if it's a birthday cake. The beach is represented by simple, clean lines: a soft beige for the sand, and gentle, stylized turquoise waves in the background under a pale blue sky. The scene is clean, with plenty of negative space. Centered above the couple is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao" in a beautiful, elegant, and readable handwritten cursive script.
